The strongest emotion I ever felt _ Death
.
I never really knew how
It felt like
To be alive
Until death came to me
Unannounced,
Silently
And at that very moment
I came to know
How it felt
To be"not alive"
That's when I realised
I was alive, all my life
But
No wonders that it was too late
.
And it took me a whole lifetime
~Zara Urooj
